c: 7
v: 44
t: "Abantu bo mu Ijuru bazahamagara abo mu muriro bababwira bati \"Rwose twasanze ibyo Nyagasani wacu yadusezeranyije ari ukuri; ese na mwe mwasanze ibyo Nyagasani wanyu yabasezeranyije ari ukuri\"? Bazavuga bati \"Yego\". Nuko umuhamagazi atangarize hagati yabo ko umuvumo wa Allah uri ku banyabyaha"